Package alexatesting

JUnit support to provide Alexa voice user interface test data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataAskResponseTest
    JUnit tests for TestDataAskResponse class.
    DataRequestTest
    JUnit tests for TestDataRequest class.
    DataTellResponseTest
    JUnit tests for TestDataTellResponse class.
    TestDataAskResponse
    For JUnit testing, create JSON responses that we expect will match to the actual JSON output from our application.
    TestDataGeneralResponse  
    TestDataRequest
    For JUnit testing, create JSON requests (conforming to what our application sees from the Alexa service) to use as test input for our application.
    TestDataTellResponse
    For JUnit testing, create JSON responses that we expect will match to the actual JSON output from our application.
    TestDataUtterance
    For JUnit testing, a helper class to make it easier to test dialogs between the user and our Alexa skill.

Package alexatesting Description

JUnit support to provide Alexa voice user interface test data. Provide expected Alexa requests and responses (TestData* classes) for comparison to actual test results from running our application's voice user interface. Also provides JUnit tests of these requests and responses (*Test classes).
Author:
J. Todd Baldwin
